      <para id="id12456498">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
      <para id="id12456503">_____________________________________________________________________</para>
      <para id="id12456509">2.2 Calculate the perimeter of each shape (remember the units). Write the name of each shape, followed by the answer.</para>
